descriptionHtml:
It’s cool to change the world. Take effec2ve sustainable ac2on, measure your unique impact,
track and share your progress. Our app is used by ci2zens, organisa2ons and governments
around the world who want to influence posi2ve and sustainable change for society, the
environment, and the economy. Champion sustainability and become an impact leader.
Social Media for Social Good – Global Impact is reinven2ng the way we create and celebrate
sustainability.
With Global Impact, you:
Track and measure your impact
Adopt daily sustainable habits
Challenge and compete with friends
Get rewarded for doing good
Showcase your success and share your journey
Here’s how it works:
-Call to Ac8on-
Take effec2ve ac2on for sustainable living in a fun, easy and rewarding way so that doing good
feels good.
Know exactly how and where you can make a real difference. Access a variety of fun impacUul
challenges, discover events, campaigns, and projects around you.
Post about your sustainable lifestyle! Recycle, buy sustainable products, donate food or clothes
to those in need, support good causes, reuse, clean beaches, plant trees and ul2mately become
a global impact leader!

-Track-
Challenge yourself to keep a sustainable lifestyle streak and track your progress towards
enabling a beEer world for everyone.
Receive verified & automised real 2me impact reports with a simple click of a buEon.
Our reports feature enables everyone to:
- Track successful ac2ons, events, campaigns & projects
- Get sta2s2cs on partner and sub-organisa2ons
- Breakdown ac2vi2es to granular member level and generate specific outcomes you want to
see
Helping governments track na2onal progress and suppor2ng organisa2ons with impact
repor2ng & accoun2ng for stakeholders in a fast, simple & cost effec2ve way.
-Measure-
With every ac2on you post on Global Impact, you can automa2cally measure your unique
change in the world with immediate impact sta2s2cs. All ac2ons are captured to calculate
impact outcomes through carefully curated data algorithms enabling our community to
measure individual as well as global progress for sustainable development.
-Showcase-
Individuals, Organisa2ons and Governments can showcase sustainability and measure global
progress in a transparent, collabora2ve, and accountable way. Create your own sustainability-
driven content genera2ng machine, marke2ng through powerful storytelling using tangible data
to back up true impact crea2on.
-Social Networking-
It’s all about community, connec2on, expression, and collabora2on. Form partnerships; follow
or friend other profiles; like and comment on other posts; share and engage with impact
content that interests you.
Help your country achieve sustainability by engaging with likeminded people crea2ng posi2ve
change.
-Gamification-
Using concepts such as gamification and social currency to incentivise action and reward those
that do good. Compete in the global race for good against friends; within challenges, in
organisations and in your country.
Get ranked with a Global Impact Score and be rewarded with badges and tokens. Rewards
coming soon: sustainable products and services.
Where technology meets humanity. Whatever gets measured gets achieved. Whatever gets
achieved gets rewarded.
Be part of a global community creating legacy and disrupting the status quo. We believe that
social media should celebrate people that make a positive impact in the world. We believe it’s
cool to do good.
JOIN THE SOCIAL MEDIA REVOLUTION FOR SUSTAINABILITY.

“The ideal social network that empowers people and organisations to become champions of
sustainability”. - Minister of Tourism Seychelles

Featured in World Expo Dubai “Best Practice Area: Spotlighting Solutions Towards the Global
Goals”.
